Package: bikerentaldata
Title: Historical U.S. Bike-Share Trip Data Tools
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R:
    c(
      person(
        given = "Christopher",
        family = "Odoom",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "odoomchristopher22@gmail.com"
      )
    )
Description: Discovers, downloads, and standardizes official historical trip
    archives from Capital Bikeshare, Citi Bike, Divvy, and Bay Wheels. It also
    summarizes station locations, prepares daily Capital Bikeshare analysis
    data with weather and calendar variables, and validates processed data.
    The package contains processing code but does not redistribute the full
    third-party datasets.
